        <div class="content-sections">
          <section class="intro-section">
            <p>
              MAC Paving and Sealcoating proudly serves homeowners and
              businesses across <strong
                >nine counties in Northern New Jersey</strong
              >. Our comprehensive coverage area includes <strong
                >Passaic, Bergen, Essex, Morris, Middlesex, Union, Somerset,
                Hudson, and Sussex</strong
              > counties, making us one of the most trusted paving contractors in
              the region.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="service-coverage">
            <h2>Complete Paving Services Across Northern NJ</h2>
            <p>
              With over <strong>15 years of experience</strong>, we've completed
              thousands of residential and commercial projects throughout our
              service territory. Our mobile crews are strategically positioned
              to provide
              <strong>fast response times</strong> and competitive pricing across
              all nine counties we serve.
            </p>

            <div class="services-grid">
              <div class="service-item">
                <h3>Asphalt Paving Services</h3>
                <ul>
                  <li>New driveway installation</li>
                  <li>Asphalt resurfacing and overlay</li>
                  <li>Driveway replacement</li>
                  <li>Parking lot construction</li>
                  <li>Private road paving</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="service-item">
                <h3>Sealcoating and Maintenance</h3>
                <ul>
                  <li>Professional sealcoating application</li>
                  <li>Crack filling and repair</li>
                  <li>Line striping and marking</li>
                  <li>Pothole repair</li>
                  <li>Preventive maintenance plans</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="service-item">
                <h3>Concrete and Hardscaping</h3>
