                  <li>Concrete sidewalks and walkways</li>
                  <li>Driveway aprons and transitions</li>
                  <li>Decorative paver installation</li>
                  <li>Belgium block edging</li>
                  <li>Concrete curbing systems</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

