                Chester, Boonton, Denville
              </p>
              <p>
                Morris County's upscale communities demand the highest quality
                paving services. We're experienced in working with homeowners'
                associations and meeting strict aesthetic guidelines while
                delivering durable, long-lasting results.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="county-info">
              <h3>Middlesex County</h3>
              <p>
                <strong>Key Cities:</strong> Edison, Woodbridge, Piscataway, East
                Brunswick, Old Bridge, Monroe, Cranbury
              </p>
