                City, Weehawken, North Bergen
              </p>
              <p>
                Hudson County's urban environment presents unique challenges
                that our experienced team handles expertly. We specialize in
                tight-space installations, urban drainage solutions, and
                coordinating with municipal requirements.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="county-info">
              <h3>Sussex County</h3>
              <p>
                <strong>Key Cities:</strong> Newton, Sparta, Hopatcong, Vernon, Franklin,
                Hamburg, Andover
              </p>
              <p>
                Sussex County's rural and mountainous terrain requires
                specialized equipment and techniques. Our team is experienced in
